{"tid":1893160,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港要當個棋子 還是塞子，這是700萬人民要決定的","createTime":"2020-02-23T05:05:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-23T16:27:34.000Z","uid":52658,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d9af5c29328ad2dd3d456844aa388a40488fce7b","tid":1893160,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T05:05:08.000Z","msg":"大家都知道中美 就像兩個下象棋的<br />\n兩個棋子在下棋<br />\n如果香港只是當一個車馬炮兵卒<br />\n時間一到 價值沒有就丟掉了<br />\n<br />\n還是我們換一個角色<br />\n泡個澡 當個塞子<br />\n<br />\n棋子 還是塞子<br />\n塞子必須有水 要泡澡<br />\n必須有浴缸 <br />\n水很重要量大 浴缸要很大<br />\n沒有這個小塞子<br />\n你今天晚上就沒有辦法泡澡<br />\n<br />\n香港是棋子 還是塞子<br />\n這是香港700萬人要決定的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b69b47186a29eac1690e53a107f55f2fbf315f1","tid":1893160,"uid":128616,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T05:06:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"99a26aaed536b3861380a3b85a65fa5d6c40d6fe","tid":1893160,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0b69b47186a29eac1690e53a107f55f2fbf315f1","tid":1893160,"uid":128616,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T05:06:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T05:10:25.000Z","msg":"所以我才會說 努力靠自己<br />\n區域聯防 共同聯防<br />\n集中力量<br />\n香港安全 人民有錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19575ed0378801269153b4985cd748496f9eedc5","tid":1893160,"uid":345458,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T05:10:30.000Z","msg":"即時13:00<br />\n全世界入嚟推呢個post上熱門！<br />\n<br />\n(煲大佢!!!) 白領工會有手足因罷工被OK便利店解僱！！嚴正譴責當局無理打壓，製造白色恐佈！！全城追擊OK便利店！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1893153\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1893153</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e2dd207424c2432d731422e9a760c997e579ebf6","tid":1893160,"uid":11013,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T05:11:41.000Z","msg":"幫